      <title>德意志银行按需增加杠杆贷款风险转移</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/deutsche-bank-increases-leveraged-loan-risk-transfer-on-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于投资者需求强劲，德意志银行将重大风险转移规模增加了 10 亿美元。]]></description>
