    <item>
      <title>高盛称消费者正在选择性消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/consumers-are-spending-selectively-goldman-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛董事总经理凯特·麦克沙恩表示，消费者“相对稳定”，但在应对通货膨胀率上升多年后，他们的消费更加谨慎。她在纽约高盛年度零售大会前接受了彭博社丽莎·阿布拉莫维茨的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/consumers-are-spending-selectively-goldman-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 13:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国贸易逆差扩大至 788 亿美元，创两年来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-trade-deficit-widens-to-78-8-billion-largest-in-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受商品进口激增推动，以及企业在可能发生的码头工人罢工之前加大力度确保充足供应，美国贸易逆差在 7 月份扩大至两年来最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-trade-deficit-widens-to-78-8-billion-largest-in-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:31:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求不足导致沃尔沃汽车下调电动汽车目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/volvo-car-walks-back-electric-push-after-disappointing-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔沃汽车公司放弃了本世纪末只销售全电动汽车的目标，由于需求减弱，该公司成为最新一家放弃电动汽车目标的汽车制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/volvo-car-walks-back-electric-push-after-disappointing-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦金属交易所 (LME) 采取措施推动市场改革，促进电子交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所（London Metal Exchange）正计划采取措施，促进其月度合约的电子交易，此举可能会减少其独特的三个月滚动合约的活动，该合约是全球金属行业的基准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼企业首次发行零售债券需求强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/adani-enterprises-kicks-off-first-bond-sale-aimed-at-individuals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在去年遭受残酷的卖空者攻击后，阿达尼企业集团寻求实现其融资基础多元化，其首次面向个人投资者发行的债券现已开放认购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/adani-enterprises-kicks-off-first-bond-sale-aimed-at-individuals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
